4) Security, Risk, and Regulatory Disclaimers
---------------------------------------------
- No Custody: This project does not take custody of user funds or private keys.
- Read-Only Posture: Public endpoints and example proxies are intended for
  read-only access to XRPL; do not rely on them for trading or custody.
- Not Investment Advice: Nothing here constitutes investment, legal, tax, or
  regulatory advice. Use at your own risk.
- No Warranties on Data: Live prices, order books, and status snapshots may be
  stale, incomplete, or wrong. Always verify on-ledger independently.
- Jurisdiction & Compliance: You are responsible for complying with applicable
  laws (including sanctions/export controls, AML/KYC obligations, and digital
  assets regulations) in your jurisdiction.
- No Securities Offering: XRBC is presented as a community token on XRPL.
  Classification may vary by jurisdiction; consult qualified counsel.


